{"tid":2042502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波：美取消特別關稅待遇對香港實際影響較小  特區已有充足應對準備","createTime":"2020-05-30T00:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T01:22:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"50ca8953a6fc897c12198f52732db7602fe28ac8","tid":2042502,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:55:43.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波表示，美國單方面取消對港特別關稅待遇對香港實際影響較小，特區政府亦已經為美國可能對香港採取的各種經濟制裁措施，作出充足應對準備。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波指美國的舉措最大影響可能是衝擊對投資者信心，而香港的股票、期貨和貨幣市場都十分冷靜，未出現大幅波動，港幣匯率強勁，亦未監測到資金大規模外流。<br />\n<br />\n他指目前香港本土生產並出口到美國市場的貨物，只佔本港總出口量不到0.1%，取消特別關稅待遇對實際影響較小，如果美國在獨立關稅地位、敏感技術進口和聯繫匯率三方面對香港作出打擊，香港都不會受到嚴重影響。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2020-05/30/41730.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"f8fa98d82fb9bd52f30ccfef912f23740293ca0a","tid":2042502,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:56:41.000Z","msg":"白粉波：沒事兒 沒事兒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fada50af1c195405c5ac9bc3c5cb4379027fc0a9","tid":2042502,"uid":69650,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:57:57.000Z","msg":"之前諗住波波上位無咩好事<br />\n依家諗返起都唔知好定壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be6eecd54160c8d117ff8d4a3b4082254193191","tid":2042502,"uid":10290,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:58:18.000Z","msg":"佢冇錯<br />\n夜期都冇反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad556845cc25704f2464feedb0283bf2eeadf91d","tid":2042502,"uid":358086,"like":1,"